      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.Item.Dysu4F8licjEb2FY]{Vanguard Discipline}</p>\n<p>You can manipulate entropy around your enemies’ attacks. As a reaction when you or an ally is targeted with an attack originating within 100 feet, you can spend 1 Entropy Point to impose a –2 penalty on the attack roll. If the attack is coming from a creature, that creature can attempt a Will saving throw to negate this effect. Once you’ve targeted an attacker with disruption, you can’t target the same attacker with this ability again for 24 hours.</p>"
